{
  "number": 80,
  "name": "سُورَةُ عَبَسَ",
  "englishName": "Abasa",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "(The Prophet) frowned and turned away,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Because there came to him the blind man (interrupting).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "But what could tell thee but that perchance he might grow (in spiritual understanding)?-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Or that he might receive admonition, and the teaching might profit him?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "As to one who regards Himself as self-sufficient,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "To him dost thou attend;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Though it is no blame to thee if he grow not (in spiritual understanding).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "But as to him who came to thee striving earnestly,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And with fear (in his heart),",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Of him wast thou unmindful.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "By no means (should it be so)! For it is indeed a Message of instruction:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "Therefore let whoso will, keep it in remembrance.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "(It is) in Books held (greatly) in honour,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Exalted (in dignity), kept pure and holy,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "(Written) by the hands of scribes-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Honourable and Pious and Just.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Woe to man! What hath made him reject Allah;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "From what stuff hath He created him?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "From a sperm-drop: He hath created him, and then mouldeth him in due proportions;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "Then doth He make His path smooth for him;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Then He causeth him to die, and putteth him in his grave;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Then, when it is His Will, He will raise him up (again).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "By no means hath he fulfilled what Allah hath commanded him.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Then let man look at his food, (and how We provide it):",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "For that We pour forth water in abundance,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "And We split the earth in fragments,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And produce therein corn,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "And Grapes and nutritious plants,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And Olives and Dates,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And enclosed Gardens, dense with lofty trees,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And fruits and fodder,-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "For use and convenience to you and your cattle.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "At length, when there comes the Deafening Noise,-",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "That Day shall a man flee from his own brother,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "And from his mother and his father,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And from his wife and his children.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Each one of them, that Day, will have enough concern (of his own) to make him indifferent to the others.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "Some faces that Day will be beaming,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "Laughing, rejoicing.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And other faces that Day will be dust-stained,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "Blackness will cover them:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Such will be the Rejecters of Allah, the doers of iniquity.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}